RPC::ExtDirect::Client::Async
=============================

    This module implements a fully asynchronous Ext.Direct client based on
    AnyEvent::HTTP. It can be used with any event loop supported by
    AnyEvent.

INSTALLATION

    To install this module type the following:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make && make test
        make install

